4 A BILL FOR AN ACT ENTITLED: “AN ACT REVISING THE COAL SEVERANCE TAX COAL WASHING
5 CREDIT; EXTENDING THE TERMINATION DATE OF THE CREDIT; PROVIDING THAT THE CONTRACT
6 SALES PRICE EXCLUDES COAL WASHING COSTS BASED ON THE PRICE OF COAL; AMENDING
7 SECTION 15-35-102, MCA; AMENDING SECTION 7, CHAPTER 433, LAWS OF 2009, AND SECTION 352,
8 CHAPTER 1, LAWS OF 2015; AND PROVIDING AN IMMEDIATE EFFECTIVE DATE.”
9
10 BE IT ENACTED BY THE LEGISLATURE OF THE STATE OF MONTANA:
